author: coheigea
msg: - Removed unnecessary BinarySecurity construction in the BSTProcessor
- Changed the SignatureProcessor to first ask the BSTProcessor for the certs...this should improve performance a good bit.

author: tabish
msg: Adds library initialization and shutdown methods to the Decaf library which accept the args passed to the process in order to later support setting system properties in the Decaf Runtime and adds an new init method the the AMQCPP library init code to allow this also.  Cleanup in thread pool to not always allocate a global pool, only do it once one is requested.
